Based on my thorough exploration of `/Users/mike/github/sw-embed/cor24-rs`, here are the findings:

### 1. UART Type Definition

**No dedicated `UartLog` or `UartLogEntry` type exists.** UART functionality is integrated into the `IoState` struct at `/Users/mike/github/sw-embed/cor24-rs/src/cpu/state.rs:53`.

