- No transaction log with metadata (no direction, cycle, or byte-level tracking)
- No coalescing or grouping logic
- Simple scalar fields track state (busy flags, dropped count, overflow)
- Output cleared on reset via `IoState::new()`
- Exposed via simple getter/setter methods to WASM and CLI
- Well-tested for basic functionality but no dump/export feature

